    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Malayopotamon weh sp. nov., holotype male (15.5 × 12.1 mm) (MZB), Pulau Weh, Sumatra. A, overall dorsal view; B, dorsal view of carapace; C, frontal view of carapace." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229086>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Malayopotamon weh sp. nov., holotype male (15.5 × 12.1 mm) (MZB), Pulau Weh, Sumatra. A, left third maxilliped; B, outer view of right major chela; C, outer view of left minor chela; D, anterior thoracic sternum and male abdomen; E, male abdomen and thoracic sternum; F, posterior part of carapace showing abdomen (first somite detached from carapace)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229086/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229087>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Malayopotamon weh sp. nov., holotype male (15.5 × 12.1 mm) (MZB), Pulau Weh, Sumatra. A, left G 1, ventral view; B, terminal segment of left G 1, ventral view; C, terminal segment of left G 1, dorsal view; D, left G 2. Scales: A, D = 1.0 mm; B, C = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229084>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Malayopotamon weh sp. nov., holotype male (15.5 × 12.1 mm) (MZB), Pulau Weh, Sumatra. Colours in life (photographs: Daniel Ng)." ;
